title: Exclude Weekends in Your Todo Items in Org Agenda
tags: @zettel _method orgmode orgagenda
roam-id: 9c175313-dc3d-4fe0-a781-d5795058aa04
type: text/markdown

``` org
* TODO Wake Up
   SCHEDULED: <%%(and (not (memq (calendar-day-of-week date) '(0 6))) t) 7:00>
```

this will exclude Saturday and Sunday. I also added 7:00 as hour information
